Hillview Capital Advisors, LLC  » Services

















































services








Wealth Management 


Hillview provides a full range of capabilities associated with a dedicated family office. One of our differentiating characteristics in the industry is our approach to creating customized solutions for clients.
Our focus on the delivery of holistic planning services—a deep understanding of a client’s situation, including tax, philanthropy, wealth transfer and personal objectives—enables us to develop comprehensive wealth management plans that align a client’s objectives with appropriate wealth management strategies.


Our approach differs in the simple but seldom-practiced notion that only a deep and personal understanding of an individual can lead to the perfect fit in a custom-tailored financial plan.  Each of our clients works directly with a partner of the firm, supported by a  dedicated client service team.
We understand the complexities that come with managing substantial wealth, and believe that close coordination and thoughtful collaboration with other professional advisors is essential to achieving our clients’ goals. In those instances we are able to provide customizable portfolio  aggregation, secure document management, consolidated portfolio and performance reporting, and support coordinated interactions and communications on our clients’ behalf. Hillview’s philosophy, culture and process have been seamlessly integrated to put clients’ interests first.















Services include:


WEALTH PLANNING

– Preparation of Comprehensive Wealth Management Plan
– Cash Flow Management
– Tax Management
– Estate Planning and Wealth Transfer Strategic Advice
– Insurance Review and Oversight
– Coordination with other Professional Advisors



INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT

– Development of Investment Policy Statement
– Asset Allocation and Investment Execution

Strategic Asset Allocation
Ongoing Monitoring
Tactical Rebalancing

– Investment Strategy Research
– Manager Due Diligence and Selection
– Risk Management
– Fee and Liquidity Analysis



REPORTING & ADMINSTRATION

– Consolidated Performance Reporting
– 24/7 Online Account and Document Vault Access
– Quarterly Asset Allocation Updates
– White Papers
– Wealth Education
– Family Meeting Facilitation
– Multigenerational Advice












Outsourced CIO 


At Hillview, we understand the investment challenges that face institutional clients. For almost two decades, we have offered foundations and endowments customized asset management solutions that are aligned with each organization’s unique mission, performance objectives and management culture.
Our firm has a long history of providing clients with high-caliber, cost-effective investment guidance and execution, as well as ongoing portfolio risk management.


Each of Hillview’s institutional clients is serviced by a team, led by a partner of the firm, that is dedicated to assisting trustees execute their fiduciary responsibilities. The principals of our firm have extensive experience in the nonprofit sector and actively devote their time and resources as board members and as advisors to national and local charitable organizations.












